f\":\"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/845777\"}}}},{\"score\":12.833665,\"show\":{\"id\":294,\"url\":\"http://www.tvmaze.com/shows/294/the-night-shift\",\"name\":\"The Night Shift\",\"type\":\"Scripted\",\"language\":\"English\",\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Action\",\"Medical\"],\"status\":\"Ended\",\"runtime\":60,\"premiered\":\"2014-05-27\",\"officialSite\":\"http://www.nbc.com/the-night-shift\",\"schedule\":{\"time\":\"22:00\",\"days\":[\"Thursday\"]},\"rating\":{\"average\":8.1},\"weight\":90,\"network\":{\"id\":1,\"name\":\"NBC\",\"country\":{\"name\":\"United States\",\"code\":\"US\",\"timezone\":\"America/New_York\"}},\"webChannel\":null,\"externals\":{\"tvrage\":35812,\"thetvdb\":269640,\"imdb\":\"tt2477230\"},\"image\":{\"medium\":\"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/126/315025.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/126/315025.jpg\"},\"summary\":\"<p>Welcome to <b>The Night Shift</b>, where the toughest and craziest cases always seem to come through the door. Every shift is a fight between the heroic efforts of saving lives and the hard truths of running an underfunded hospital.</p><p>At San Antonio Memorial, the men and women who work the night shift are an irreverent and special breed, particularly adrenaline junkie TC Callahan. After three grueling tours of duty in Afghanistan, TC is about to learn that his toughest battles will be fought right here at home.</p>\",\"updated\":1579559016,\"_links\":{\"self\":{\"href\":\"http://api.tvmaze.com/shows/294\"},\"previousepisode\":{\"href\":\"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1163474\"}}}},{\"score\":12.335071,\"show\":{\"id\":3699,\"url\":\"http://www.tvmaze.com/shows/3699/night-gallery\",\"name\":\"Night Gallery\",\"type\":\"Scripted\",\"language\":\"English\",\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Horror\",\"Supernatural\"],\"status\":\"Ended\",\"runtime\":30,\"premiered\":\"1969-11-08\",\"officialSite\":null,\"schedule\":{\"time\":\"22:00\",\"days\":[\"Wednesday\"]},\"rating\":{\"average\":null},\"weight\":54,\"network\":{\"id\":1,\"name\":\"NBC\",\"country\":{\"name\":\"United States\",\"code\":\"US\",\"timezone\":\"America/New_York\"}},\"webChannel\":null,\"externals\":{\"tvrage\":null,\"thetvdb\":70382,\"imdb\":\"tt0065327\"},\"image\":{\"medium\":\"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/18/47465.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/18/47465.jpg\"},\"summary\":\"<p>Rod Serling returns to anthology television as the host of <b>Night Gallery</b>, a three-season show where each story revolves around a mysterious and ominous painting hanging in an empty gallery. Mr. Serling provides the opening and closing narration to these stories, typically tales of horror and the supernatural. During the first season, the hour-long series features several shorter stories, some of which are comedic blackout sketches. The show was subsequently cut down to a half-hour, and in syndication was mixed with episodes of the TV series <i>The Sixth Sense</i>.</p>\",\"updated\":1574379160,\"_links\":{\"self\":{\"href\":\"http://api.tvmaze.com/shows/3699\"},\"previousepisode\":{\"href\":\"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1008835\"}}}},{\"score\":11.977217,\"show\":{\"id\":31428,\"url\":\"http://www.tvmaze.com/shows/31428/all-night\",\"name\":\"All Night\",\"type\":\"Scripted\",\"language\":\"English\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\"],\"status\":\"Ended\",\"runtime\":30,\"premiered\":\"2018-05-11\",\"officialSite\":\"https://www.hulu.com/all-night\",\"schedule\":{\"time\":\"\",\"days\":[\"Friday\"]},\"rating\":{\"average\":7.8},\"weight\":62,\"network\":null,\"webChannel\":{\"id\":2,\"name\":\"Hulu\",\"country\":{\"name\":\"United States\",\"code\":\"US\",\"timezone\":\"America/New_York\"}},\"externals\":{\"tvrage\":null,\"thetvdb\":346001,\"imdb\":\"tt7292950\"},\"image\":{\"medium\":\"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/155/388118.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/155/388118.jpg\"},\"summary\":\"<p>After their graduation, the class of 2018 gathers to celebrate their last night together at their local rec center for \\\"Grad Night,\\\" an all-night party with dancing, karaoke, games—and a rule that no one can come in or out for twelve full hours. For most the night signals their last chance to accomplish some high school dream: Nerdy Cody wants to make his mark on the school, and popular Roni wants to finally lose her virginity to her boyfriend Oz. Valedictorian Melinda plans to sneakily sell alcohol to her classmates at the party to pay her tuition, and every-girl Deanna gets ready to finally admit her feelings for her best friend Fig, who only has eyes for Roni. As the night goes on, the kids' quests overlap, intertwine, and -in some cases- implode. What would you do with your last night in high school?</p>\",\"updated\":1584839348,\"_links\":{\"self\":{\"href\":\"http://api.tvmaze.com/shows/31428\"},\"previousepisode\":{\"href\":\"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1461722\"}}}},{\"score\":10.880826,\"show\":{\"id\":361,\"url\":\"http://www.tvmaze.com/shows/361/saturday-night-live\",\"name\":\"Saturday Night Live\",\"type\":\"Variety\",\"language\":\"English\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Music\"],\"status\":\"Running\",\"runtime\":90,\"premiered\":\"1975-10-11\",\"officialSite\":\"http://www.nbc.com/saturday-night-live\",\"schedule\":{\"time\":\"23:29\",\"days\":[\"Saturday\"]},\"rating\":{\"average\":6.3},\"weight\":97,\"network\":{\"id\":1,\"name\":\"NBC\",\"country\":{\"name\":\"United States\",\"code\":\"US\",\"timezone\":\"America/New_York\"}},\"webChannel\":null,\"externals\":{\"tvrage\":5098,\"thetvdb\":76177,\"imdb\":\"tt0072562\"},\"image\":{\"medium\":\"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/2/5468.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/2/5468.jpg\"},\"summary\":\"<p><b>Saturday Night Live</b> is an Emmy Award-winning late-night comedy showcase.</p><p>Since its inception in 1975, \\\"SNL\\\" has launched the careers of many of the brightest comedy performers of their generation. As The New York Times noted on the occasion of the show's Emmy-winning 25th Anniversary special in 1999, \\\"in defiance of both time and show business convention, 'SNL' is still the most pervasive influence on the art of comedy in contemporary culture.\\\" At the close of the century, \\\"Saturday Night Live\\\" placed seventh on Entertainment Weekly's list of the Top 100 Entertainers of the past fifty years.</p>\",\"updated\":1586713329,\"_links\":{\"self\":{\"href\":\"http://api.tvmaze.com/shows/361\"},\"previousepisode\":{\"href\":\"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1813450\"}}}},{\"score\":10.826691,\"show\":{\"id\":1489,\"url\":\"http://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1489/night-court\",\"name\":\"Night Court\",\"type\":\"Scripted\",\"language\":\"English\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\"],\"status\":\"Ended\",\"runtime\":30,\"premiered\":\"1984-01-04\",\"officialSite\":null,\"schedule\":{\"time\":\"20:30\",\"days\":[\"Thursday\"]},\"rating\":{\"average\":7.4},\"weight\":82,\"network\":{\"id\":1,\"name\":\"NBC\",\"country\":{\"name\":\"United States\",\"code\":\"US\",\"timezone\":\"America/New_York\"}},\"webChannel\":null,\"externals\":{\"tvrage\":4663,\"thetvdb\":70812,\"imdb\":\"tt0086770\"},\"image\":{\"medium\":\"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/8/21196.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/8/21196.jpg\"},\"summary\":\"<p>A young and unusual judge arrives in Manhattan's <b>Night Court</b> and begins deciding cases in a most unusual manner, much to the horror of his court clerk and all else in the courtroom.</p>\",\"updated\":1586646514,\"_links\":{\"self\":{\"href\":\"http://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1489\"},\"previousepisode\":{\"href\":\"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/134435\"}}}},{\"score\":10.825388,\"show\":{\"id\":1789,\"url\":\"http://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1789/friday-night-dinner\",\"name\":\"Friday Night Dinner\",\"type\":\"Scripted\",\"language\":\"English\",\"genres\":[\"Comedy\",\"Family\"],\"status\":\"Running\",\"runtime\":35,\"premiered\":\"2011-02-25\",\"officialSite\":\"http://www.channel4.com/programmes/friday-night-dinner\",\"schedule\":{\"time\":\"22:00\",\"days\":[\"Friday\"]},\"rating\":{\"average\":8.4},\"weight\":96,\"network\":{\"id\":45,\"name\":\"Channel 4\",\"country\":{\"name\":\"United Kingdom\",\"code\":\"GB\",\"timezone\":\"Europe/London\"}},\"webChannel\":null,\"externals\":{\"tvrage\":27623,\"thetvdb\":235081,\"imdb\":\"tt1844923\"},\"image\":{\"medium\":\"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/medium_portrait/43/109637.jpg\",\"original\":\"http://static.tvmaze.com/uploads/images/original_untouched/43/109637.jpg\"},\"summary\":\"<p>For the Goodman family, <b>Friday Night Dinner</b> is just like Sunday lunch: just take two days away, change the meal to dinner, and you've pretty much got it. Adam and his brother, Jonny, view Friday night dinner as a necessary annoyance - necessary because they get fed, and annoying because, well, they have to spend the evening with mum and dad.</p>\",\"updated\":1586728806,\"_links\":{\"self\":{\"href\":\"http://api.tvmaze.com/shows/1789\"},\"previousepisode\":{\"href\":\"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1824894\"},\"nextepisode\":{\"href\":\"http://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/1827140\"}}}},{\"score\":10.804054,\"show\":{\"id\":1284,\"url\":\"http://www.tvmaze.com/shows/1284/sports-night\",\"name\":\"Sports Night\",\"type\":\"Scripted\",\"language\":\"English\",\"genres\":[\"Drama\",\"Comedy\",\"Sports\"],\"status\":\"Ended\",\"runtime\":30,\"premiered\":\"1998-09-22\",\"officialSite\":null,\"schedule\":{\"time\":\"21:30\",\"days\":[\"Tuesday\"]},\"rating\":{\"average\":7.3},\"weight\":0,\"network\":{\"id\":3,\"name\":\"ABC\",\"country\":{\"name\":\"United States\",\"code\":\"US\",\"timezone\":\"America/New_York\"}},\"webChannel\":null,\"externals\":{\"tvrage\":5309,\"thetvdb\":71969,\